Package: ecodown
Title: Publish package documents in Quarto
Version: 0.0.0.9003
Authors@R: 
    person(
    given = "Edgar", 
    family = "Ruiz", 
    email = "edgararuiz@gmail.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Makes it possible for your R package's documentation to be published 
    in a Quarto site. The vision for this package is that it is used to 
    document a group of related packages that will be published to a single 
    Quarto site.  
License: MIT + file LICENSE
